item.title: About
item.description: Hello There Hi, my name is Daniel Jackson. I live in New York and am a software engineer by trade. This blog is a fun and constructive way to get my thoughts in order and reinforce what I have and am learning. Since this is for self-betterment and not self-advertisement, I’ll keep this short. I studied Computer Science and Applied Math Economics which is what most posts will be on.
